WEBVTT

00:03.069 --> 00:04.570
<i>In the last episode of</i> Soap,

00:04.571 --> 00:06.071
<i>Danny and Burt</i>
<i>got the ransom money,</i>

00:06.072 --> 00:07.573
<i>and after the kidnappers get it,</i>

00:07.574 --> 00:10.075
<i>hopefully, Elaine will get home.</i>

00:10.076 --> 00:12.578
<i>Corinne has learned</i>
<i>she's five months pregnant,</i>

00:12.579 --> 00:14.079
<i>which she doesn't get,</i>

00:14.080 --> 00:16.582
<i>because she and Tim</i>
<i>only got married last month,</i>

00:16.583 --> 00:19.084
<i>and no one got near her</i>
<i>before that.</i>

00:19.085 --> 00:22.087
<i>Detective Donohue told Jessica</i>
<i>that although he loves her,</i>

00:22.088 --> 00:24.590
<i>he'll get Chester back for her,</i>

00:24.591 --> 00:27.593
<i>but then,</i>
<i>he'll get her away Chester.</i>

00:27.594 --> 00:29.094
<i>Jodie thought</i>
<i>he was getting married</i>

00:29.095 --> 00:30.596
<i>and got jilted instead.</i>

00:30.597 --> 00:32.097
<i>Don't get it?</i>

00:32.098 --> 00:33.599
<i>You will</i>
<i>after tonight's episode of...</i>

00:39.606 --> 00:42.107
<i>This is the story</i>
<i>of two sisters,</i>

00:42.108 --> 00:44.109
<i>Jessica Tate</i>

00:44.110 --> 00:46.612
<i>and Mary Campbell.</i>

00:46.613 --> 00:50.115
<i>These are the Tates,</i>

00:50.116 --> 00:53.619
<i>and these are the Campbells.</i>

00:53.620 --> 00:55.622
<i>And this is...</i> Soap.

