23:35.480 --> 23:37.982
<i>that it was one night</i>
<i>with an old fat lady?</i>

23:37.983 --> 23:40.484
<i>Does Jessica believe</i>
<i>she can be in love with two men</i>

23:40.485 --> 23:41.485
<i>at the same time?</i>

23:41.486 --> 23:42.987
<i>What will Tim do</i>

23:42.988 --> 23:44.488
<i>since he doesn't believe</i>
